fields.name: Abilities:
fields.value:
- Beep 1 key and give another player Basic defense for the night.
- Beep 2 keys to transport 2 players. You may transport yourself..
- Beep 3 keys to give someone an Invincible autovest but making them unable to use night abilities until it's broken. You may give yourself this autovest.

fields.name: Attributes:
fields.value: You will earn 1 key every night. You can use 2 abilities per night.
